data.text:
"RocKwiz Duets- Volume 3 - The Beat Goes On" is another collection of the unique duets that close each episode of RocKwiz, this DVD contains duets from Series 5 and 6. It also features some rather special surprises and has extras including introductory comments by Julia, Brian, and the Orkestra.

1. Jess Mcavoy & Charles Jenkins - The Beat Goes On

2. Kasey Chambers & Shane Nicholson - Can't Get You Out Of My Head

3. Sophie Koh & Steve Kilbey - Streets Of Your Town

4. Karina Utomo & Steve Lucas - Something In The Air

5. Abbe May & Dom Mariani - Sinister Purpose

6. Catherine Britt & Max Merritt - Slippin' Away

7. The Wolfgramm Sisters & Leo Sayer - When I Need You

8. Patience Hodgson & Broderick Smith - Time To Pretend

9. Sarah Kelly & Toby Martin - Sometimes Always

10. Taasha Coates & Pete Murray - Comes A Time

11. Wendy Matthews & Johnny Galvatron - Hold The Line

15. Eve Von Bibra & Jed Kurzel - To Love Somebody
